      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MACHX THE STRANGER (6) did a solid job when fourth from this barrier three back and has been far from disgraced from tricky draws since. This looks a suitable assignment so could return to the winners' list. TWO BLUES BLING (7) draws wide but brings some good form to the table including a Canberra win three back and second at her most recent outing at this circuit and distance. The driver has some work to do from this starting position but if things go her way she could find the winners' circle. SHES GOT A REASON (8) did a good to place from the back row when resuming at this circuit and distance then was well fancied last start but manners let her down. Draws wide but has won third-up before so should be race fit. OUR ULTIMATE BONNY (9) has claims off a win from this barrier here two back.",
